<section class="text-block  bg-white " >
      <div class="container heading-container text-block__container">
      <h2 class="block_title">            Use of reports and queries
      </h2>
    </div>
        <div class="container">
      <div class="row text-block__row image_left ">
                  <div class="col-12 text-block__body-container">
                        <p>The use of information contained in internal audit reports will be subject to the&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ifrc.org/disclaimer/">IFRC disclaimer</a>. The IFRC will not respond to public queries concerning audit reports.</p>

      
